org.sxb.http

インタフェース StreamingHttpOutputMessage.Body

  • 含まれているインタフェース:
    StreamingHttpOutputMessage

    public static interface StreamingHttpOutputMessage.Body
    Defines the contract for bodies that can be written directly to a OutputStream. It is useful with HTTP client libraries that provide indirect access to an OutputStream via a callback mechanism.

    • メソッドの概要
